OL,3,CEx-Pcs who shared 'offensive' messages
OL,4,Cin chat with Wayne Couzens lose appeals
OL,6,FTwo former police officers who shared
OL,7,F"grossly offensive" messages in a
OL,8,FWhatsApp group with Wayne Couzens have
OL,9,Flost a bid to overturn their
OL,10,Fconvictions at the High Court.
OL,12,FFormer Pcs Jonathon Cobban and Joel
OL,13,FBorders were each given a three-month
OL,14,Fjail sentence for sending grossly
OL,15,Foffensive messages on a public
OL,16,Fcommunications network.
