OL,3,CEx-Pcs who shared 'offensive' messages
OL,4,Cin chat with Wayne Couzens lose appeals
OL,6,FWestminster Magistrates' Court heard
OL,7,Fin November 2022 that the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice officers joked about raping a
OL,9,Ffemale colleague, talked about
OL,10,Ftasering children and people with
OL,11,Fdisabilities, and displayed racist
OL,12,Fviews in the group chat called "Bottle
OL,13,Fand Stoppers" which included Couzens.
OL,15,FThe messages were discovered after
OL,16,FCouzens' devices were searched after
OL,17,Fhis arrest for the kidnap, rape and
OL,18,Fmurder of 33-year-old marketing
OL,19,Fexecutive Sarah Everard in March 2020.
