OL,3,CEx-Pcs who shared 'offensive' messages
OL,4,Cin chat with Wayne Couzens lose appeals
OL,6,FAt a hearing last month, lawyers for
OL,7,Fboth men brought an appeal against
OL,8,Ftheir convictions and sentences at the
OL,9,FHigh Court in London.
OL,11,FIn a ruling on Friday, the Lady Chief
OL,12,FJustice Baroness Carr and Mr Justice
OL,13,FSaini dismissed the appeals.
OL,15,FIn a summary of their decision,
OL,16,FBaroness Carr said the pair "could
OL,17,Fhave no reasonable expectation of
OL,18,Fprivacy" over the messages which
OL,19,F"relate to policing actions".
OL,26,@xD@]OUzD@HO]{D@AOU{D@\O]
