OL,6,FFollowing the ruling, the most senior
OL,7,Fjudge in England and Wales said the
OL,8,Ftwo men will be given 28 days "to
OL,9,Freflect maturely on their present
OL,10,Fposition" about whether to make a
OL,11,FSupreme Court bid.
OL,13,FIf the two men ` who were granted bail
OL,14,Fafter their sentencing ` decide not to
OL,15,Fmake a bid for a challenge at the UK's
OL,16,Fhighest court, they will need to
OL,17,Freturn to Westminster Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt within 10 days.
