OL,3,CEx-Pcs who shared 'offensive' messages
OL,4,Cin chat with Wayne Couzens lose appeals
OL,6,FAt the hearing on June 26, Nicholas
OL,7,FYeo, for the two men, told judges that
OL,8,Fthe offence they were convicted of
OL,9,F"does not extend to private consensual
OL,10,Fmessaging" and is instead aimed at
OL,11,Fmessages "that would not be welcomed
OL,12,Fby the addressee".
OL,14,FHe said: "If one looks at the word
OL,15,Findecent, it would be absurd to
OL,16,Fconclude that it applies to wanted
OL,17,Findecent messages."
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@JO]sD@JOUtD@QO]vD@JOUyD@SO]
