OL,6,FMr Yeo continued in written
OL,7,Fsubmissions: "It is lawful to send
OL,8,Fjokey, bombastic and iconoclastic
OL,9,Fmessages to a closed group of people
OL,10,Fwho will not be grossly offended
OL,11,Fthereby."
OL,13,FJocelyn Ledward KC, for the Director
OL,14,Fof Public Prosecutions, said there
OL,15,Fwere no errors of law in the previous
OL,16,Fjudge's decision-making and that the
OL,17,Fmen's argument over the law was
OL,18,F"fundamentally misconceived".
