OL,6,FIn another, Cobban joked about
OL,7,Fsexually abusing domestic violence
OL,8,Fsurvivors whom he said "love it...
OL,9,Fthat's why they are repeat victims
OL,10,Fmore often than not".
OL,12,FRosemary Ainslie, head of the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service's Special Crime
OL,14,FDivision, welcomed the High Court's
OL,15,Fruling.
OL,17,FShe said: "It remains unfathomable
OL,18,Fthat those tasked with upholding the
OL,19,Flaw and protecting the public could
OL,20,Fthink it right to share such grossly
OL,21,Foffensive material.
OL,26,@pD@XOUrD@TO]yD@KOU
