OL,6,F"In rejecting the appeal, the High
OL,7,FCourt has confirmed that the sending
OL,8,Fof these messages amounts to a
OL,9,Fcriminal offence.
OL,11,F"Jonathon Cobban and Joel Borders will
OL,12,Fnow finally be punished for their
OL,13,Factions.
OL,15,F"To be clear, where there is
OL,16,Fsufficient evidence and it is in the
OL,17,Fpublic interest to do so, the CPS will
OL,18,Falways prosecute communications
OL,19,Foffences."
